### Jobs API Examples

### Get all jobs
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/jobs/
Content-Type: application/json

### Get jobs with pagination
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/jobs/?page=1&page_size=10
Content-Type: application/json

### Search jobs by title or description
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/jobs/?search=developer
Content-Type: application/json

### Filter by employment type
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/jobs/?employment_type=full_time
Content-Type: application/json

### Filter by work location
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/jobs/?work_location=remote
Content-Type: application/json

### Filter by skills
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/jobs/?skills=Python,Django
Content-Type: application/json

### Filter by salary range
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/jobs/?min_salary=50000&max_salary=100000
Content-Type: application/json

### Filter by date range
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/jobs/?created_after=2024-01-01&created_before=2024-12-31
Content-Type: application/json

### Combined filters
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/jobs/?search=python&employment_type=full_time&work_location=remote&min_salary=60000
Content-Type: application/json

### Order by salary (descending)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/jobs/?ordering=-salary
Content-Type: application/json

### Order by creation date (ascending)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/jobs/?ordering=created_on
Content-Type: application/json

### Get job statistics
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/jobs/statistics/
Content-Type: application/json

### Get specific job by ID
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/jobs/1/
Content-Type: application/json

### Create new job
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/jobs/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Senior Python Developer",
  "description": "We are looking for an experienced Python developer...",
  "company_name": "Tech Corp",
  "employment_type": "full_time",
  "work_location": "remote",
  "salary": 80000,
  "skills": "Python,Django,PostgreSQL",
  "location": "Jakarta, Indonesia",
  "requirements": "5+ years experience in Python development"
}

### Update job
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/jobs/1/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Senior Python Developer - Updated",
  "description": "Updated job description...",
  "company_name": "Tech Corp",
  "employment_type": "full_time",
  "work_location": "hybrid",
  "salary": 85000,
  "skills": "Python,Django,PostgreSQL,Redis",
  "location": "Jakarta, Indonesia",
  "requirements": "5+ years experience in Python development"
}

### Partial update job
PATCH http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/jobs/1/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "salary": 90000,
  "work_location": "remote"
}

### Delete job
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/jobs/1/

### Job Assessments API Examples

### Get user's job assessments (requires authentication)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/job-assessments/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Token YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Create job assessment (requires authentication)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/job-assessments/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Token YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "job_uid": "job-uuid-here",
  "score": 85,
  "feedback": "Great job opportunity with good growth potential"
}

### Get specific job assessment
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/job-assessments/1/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Token YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Update job assessment
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/job-assessments/1/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Token YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "score": 90,
  "feedback": "Updated feedback - excellent opportunity"
}

### Delete job assessment
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/job-assessments/1/
Authorization: Token YOUR_TOKEN_HERE